OL,3,CBafta confirms honour for Matthew
OL,4,CPerry after backlash
OL,6,FBafta has confirmed Friends actor will
OL,7,Fbe honoured at the organisation's TV
OL,8,Fawards in May after he was not
OL,9,Ffeatured in the in memoriam segment at
OL,10,FSunday's film awards ceremony.
OL,12,FTed Lasso actress Hannah Waddingham
OL,13,Fperformed a pared down version of
OL,14,FCyndi Lauper's Time After Time in
OL,15,FSunday's in memoriam segment, which
OL,16,Ffeatured tributes to stars including
OL,17,FJane Birkin, Glynis Johns, Carl
OL,18,FWeathers, Julian Sands, Tom Wilkinson
OL,19,Fand Tina Turner.
