OL,4,CPerry after backlash
OL,6,FAlso featured were Harry Belafonte,
OL,7,FAlan Arkin and Sir Michael Gambon.
OL,9,FHowever, Perry, who died in October at
OL,10,Fthe age of 54, was not mentioned.
OL,12,FIn response to a user on X, formerly
OL,13,FTwitter, questioning Perry's absence
OL,14,Ffrom the segment, the organisation's
OL,15,Fofficial account said: "Matthew Perry
OL,16,Fwill be remembered in this year's TV
OL,17,FAwards ceremony."
