OL,6,FThe account also linked to the in
OL,7,Fmemoriam section on the Bafta website,
OL,8,Fwhich said Perry's Friends fame
OL,9,F"brought film opportunities, including
OL,10,FFools Rush In (1997), The Whole Nine
OL,11,FYards (2000) and its sequel, The Whole
OL,12,FTen Yards (2004), and 17 Again (2009)".
OL,14,FBafta has also confirmed TV director
OL,15,FRoy Battersby will be honoured at the
OL,16,FMay ceremony after his actress
OL,17,Fstepdaughter Kate Beckinsale .
